Unitron:


Unitron easily caught up with the Stunticon, accelerating to 230 MPH.  "So 
you want to look like an Autobot?" he armed his missile weapons.  He was 
starting to sound like an Autobot, and Unitron was sure he could find this 
impostor to the name of Megatron without Speedbreaker's help.

"That is very sad.  Are you not supposed to be a Decepticon?"
